metadata.name: The Kill
metadata.description:
I had a hope that I would be able to see one of these magnificent creatures while I was in South Africa. One day, while I was riding with the guide on the reservation there came a call across the radio that notified us that a cheetah had been spotted hunting nearby. 

We slowly drove over the area and thankfully got there after the kill had been made. It was an incredible moment to sit and watch the circle of life. 

Size 2544 x 3014 / 8.25 MB
Edition: 1/1
